#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:65
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid ""
"With this you can define how deep the solid ground is. If it is 0 then the "
"surface will be solid. If it is 0.1 then you'll have 10 cm of fluid on top "
"of solid ground. If it is 100 then the solid ground will be way deep (100m), "
"with fluid on top."
msgstr ""
"Dengan ini Anda dapat menentukan seberapa dalam permukaan padat. Jika "
"nilainya 0 maka permukaan akan padat. Jika nilainya 0.1 maka Anda akan "
"memiliki 10 cm fluida di atas permukaan padat. Jika nilainya 100 maka "
"permukaan padat akan sangat dalam (100 m), dengan fluida di atasnya."

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:67
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Strength:"
msgstr "Kekuatan:"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:68
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Strength"
msgstr "Kekuatan"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:68
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid ""
"This parameter raises or diminishes surface friction in a generic way. It is "
"here so as to be able to do quick calibrations of friction. Start with "
"having this to 1.0 and after tuning the rest of the surface variables, come "
"back and play with this."
msgstr ""
"Parameter ini menaikkan atau menurunkan gesekan permukaan secara umum. Ini "
"ada agar dapat melakukan kalibrasi gesekan dengan cepat. Mulailah dengan "
"mengaturnya ke 1.0 dan setelah menyetel variabel permukaan lainnya, kembali "
"lagi dan sesuaikan parameter ini."

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:70
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Static friction coef:"
msgstr "Koef. gesekan statis:"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:71
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Static friction coef"
msgstr "Koef. gesekan statis"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:71
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid ""
"Static friction keeps you in the same place when you are stopped on a hill. "
"In the real world this friction is always bigger than dynamic friction "
"(sliding friction). Start with 0.5 and work from there. It is better to try "
"to find some experimentally validated values for this and the rest of "
"surface friction variables in the net, and then to fine tune via strength."
msgstr ""
"Gesekan statis membuat Anda tetap di tempat saat berhenti di tanjakan. Di "
"dunia nyata, gesekan ini selalu lebih besar daripada gesekan dinamis "
"(gesekan saat meluncur). Mulailah dari 0.5 dan sesuaikan dari sana. Lebih "
"baik mencoba menemukan nilai yang tervalidasi secara eksperimen untuk ini "
"dan variabel gesekan permukaan lainnya di internet, lalu lakukan penyetelan "
"halus melalui parameter kekuatan."

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:73
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Adhesion velocity:"
msgstr "Kecepatan adhesi:"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:74
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Adhesion velocity"
msgstr "Kecepatan adhesi"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:74
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid ""
"Below this value static friction laws apply, above it dynamic friction laws "
"apply. Value should be small, in the range of 0.1-0.4 . This velocity "
"threshold is also used by fluid dynamics so you should always define it. "
"NEVER set it to 0."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah nilai ini, hukum gesekan statis berlaku; di atasnya, hukum gesekan "
"dinamis berlaku. Nilainya harus kecil, dalam kisaran 0.1-0.4. Ambang "
"kecepatan ini juga digunakan oleh dinamika fluida sehingga Anda harus selalu "
"menentukannya. JANGAN PERNAH mengaturnya ke 0."

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:76
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Dynamic friction coef:"
msgstr "Koef. gesekan dinamis:"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:77
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Dynamic friction coef"
msgstr "Koef. gesekan dinamis"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:77
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid ""
"Or sliding friction coef. It should be smaller than static friction coef. "
"This parameter defines how much friction you'll have when sliding. Try to "
"find some values for it from the net."
msgstr ""
"Atau koef. gesekan meluncur. Nilainya harus lebih kecil daripada koef. "
"gesekan statis. Parameter ini menentukan seberapa besar gesekan saat "
"meluncur. Cobalah mencari nilainya di internet."

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:79
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Hydrodynamic friction coef:"
msgstr "Koef. gesekan hidrodinamik:"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:80
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Hydrodynamic friction coef"
msgstr "Koef. gesekan hidrodinamik"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:80
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid ""
"This friction defines the added friction that you'll feel from a surface "
"that has a little film of fluid on it. It is kind of redundant with all the "
"fluid physics below, but it is here so as for experimentally validated "
"values from the net to be usable. If you decide that you'll simulate the "
"film of fluid with the more complex fluid physics below, then just set this "
"to 0."
msgstr ""
"Gesekan ini mendefinisikan gesekan tambahan yang akan Anda rasakan dari "
"permukaan yang memiliki sedikit lapisan fluida di atasnya. Ini agak redundan "
"dengan seluruh fisika fluida di bawah, tetapi disediakan agar nilai yang "
"tervalidasi secara eksperimen dari internet dapat digunakan. Jika Anda "
"memutuskan untuk mensimulasikan lapisan fluida dengan fisika fluida yang "
"lebih kompleks di bawah, maka cukup atur ini ke 0."

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:82
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Stribeck velocity:"
msgstr "Kecepatan Stribeck:"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:83
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Stribeck velocity"
msgstr "Kecepatan Stribeck"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:83
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid ""
"You'll either find stribeck velocity in the net, or the inverse (1/stribeck "
"velocity) of it described as 'stribeck coef'. It defines the shape of the "
"dynamic friction curve. Lets leave it at that. Just find some nice values "
"for it from the net."
msgstr ""
"Anda bisa menemukan kecepatan stribeck di internet, atau kebalikannya \\((1/"
"\text{kecepatan stribeck})\\) yang dijelaskan sebagai 'koef. stribeck'. Ini "
"mendefinisikan bentuk kurva gesekan dinamis. Cukup sampai di situ. Cari saja "
"nilai yang bagus untuknya dari internet."

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:85
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "alpha:"
msgstr "alpha:"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:86
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Alpha"
msgstr "Alpha"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:86
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Its usual value is 2. But you can try others."
msgstr "Nilai biasanya adalah 2. Namun Anda bisa mencoba yang lain."

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:88
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Fluid Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Fluida"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:90
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Flow behavior index:"
msgstr "Indeks perilaku aliran:"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:91
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Flow behavior index"
msgstr "Indeks perilaku aliran"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:91
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid ""
"If it is 1.0 then the fluid will behave like water. The lower you get from "
"1.0, the more like mud the fluid will behave, meaning that for small "
"velocities the fluid will resist motion and for large velocities the fluid "
"will not resist so much. The higher you get from 1.0 the more like sand the "
"fluid will behave. The bigger the velocity, the bigger the resistance of the "
"fluid (try to hit sand hard it'll feel like stone)."
msgstr ""
"Jika nilainya 1.0 maka fluida akan berperilaku seperti air. Semakin rendah "
"nilainya dari 1.0, semakin fluida berperilaku seperti lumpur, artinya pada "
"kecepatan kecil fluida akan menahan gerakan dan pada kecepatan besar fluida "
"tidak akan terlalu menahan. Semakin tinggi nilainya dari 1.0, semakin fluida "
"berperilaku seperti pasir. Semakin besar kecepatan, semakin besar resistansi "
"fluida (coba hantam pasir dengan keras, rasanya seperti batu)."

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:93
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Flow consistency:"
msgstr "Konsistensi aliran:"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:94
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Flow consistency"
msgstr "Konsistensi aliran"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:94
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid ""
"Think of it as default fluid resistance. Behavior index above changes it at "
"real time. Useful values in practice are quite large."
msgstr ""
"Anggap ini sebagai resistansi fluida default. Indeks perilaku di atas "
"mengubahnya secara real time. Nilai yang berguna dalam praktik biasanya "
"cukup besar."

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:96
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Fluid density:"
msgstr "Kerapatan fluida:"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:97
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Fluid density"
msgstr "Kerapatan fluida"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:97
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid ""
"In mud (or sand) the resistance of the fluid described by the parameters "
"above will stop you and so keep you from sinking. But for substances like "
"water it isn't the drag that stops you from sinking. Its buoyancy. This "
"parameter is here so as to keep you from sinking when you wish to simulate "
"fluids with low drag (resistance). For fluids like mud or sand you can put "
"it at 0, but it is best to keep it at some minimum value. For fluids with "
"behavior index >=1 it will behave like you are in water. For fluids with "
"behavior index <1 it'll behave like you are in mud."
msgstr ""
"Di lumpur (atau pasir), resistansi fluida yang dijelaskan oleh parameter di "
"atas akan menghentikan Anda dan dengan demikian mencegah Anda tenggelam. "
"Namun untuk zat seperti air, bukan hambatan (resistansi) yang menghentikan "
"Anda tenggelam, melainkan daya apung. Parameter ini ada agar Anda tidak "
"tenggelam ketika Anda ingin mensimulasikan fluida dengan hambatan "
"(resistansi) rendah. Untuk fluida seperti lumpur atau pasir Anda bisa "
"mengaturnya ke 0, tetapi sebaiknya tetap di nilai minimum tertentu. Untuk "
"fluida dengan indeks perilaku \\(\\ge 1\\) ini akan berperilaku seperti Anda "
"berada di air. Untuk fluida dengan indeks perilaku \\(< 1\\) ini akan "
"berperilaku seperti Anda berada di lumpur."

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:99
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Drag anisotropy:"
msgstr "Anisotropi hambatan:"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:100
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid "Drag anisotropy"
msgstr "Anisotropi hambatan"

#: gui/panels/GUI_FrictionSettings.cpp:100
msgctxt "FrictionSettings"
msgid ""
"This parameter is for making it easier(cheating) to get out from mud. To get "
"stuck in real mud isn't fun at all, so this makes the mud push up. Ranges in "
"this parameter are from 0 to 1 . If you set it at 1 then you'll get real "
"mud. For values from 0 to 1, the behavior goes from real mud to easy mud "
"depending on this parameter and the value of Adhesion velocity. For velocity "
"0 real mud it is. For velocity >= adhesion velocity easy mud it is."
msgstr ""
"Parameter ini untuk memudahkan (curang) agar bisa keluar dari lumpur. "
"Terjebak di lumpur sungguhan sama sekali tidak menyenangkan, jadi ini "
"membuat lumpur mendorong ke atas. Rentang parameter ini dari 0 hingga 1. "
"Jika Anda mengaturnya ke 1 maka Anda akan mendapatkan lumpur sungguhan. "
"Untuk nilai 0 hingga 1, perilaku berubah dari lumpur sungguhan ke lumpur "
"yang mudah, bergantung pada parameter ini dan nilai Kecepatan adhesi. Untuk "
"kecepatan 0: lumpur sungguhan. Untuk kecepatan \\(\\ge\\) kecepatan adhesi: "
"lumpur mudah."

